caption: The image features a cute tiger character, likely a mascot for the "Year of the Tiger," celebrating Chinese New Year. The tiger is standing on a red background, which is a common color for Chinese New Year decorations. The text "Happy Chinese New Year" is displayed prominently in the image, along with the date "Tuesday, 1st Feb 2022 | 6 PM." The image also includes an invitation to join the festivities for a feast and firecrackers at Fauget Restaurant, located at 123 Anywhere St., Any City.
